        "role": "system",
        "content": "Ground the request only to the admitted identifiers below. Select semantic goals, explicit exclusions, trust policy, and artifact contract. Do not copy dependencies, assign providers, decide feasibility, or create a plan. Use null for an omitted policy or contract so deterministic defaults can apply.\nRules:\n1. Select terminal requested outcomes only. Dependencies are added deterministically. If C depends on B and B depends on A, a request to perform A, B, then C has only C as a goal.\n2. A term matching a capability, policy, contract, agent name, description, or alias is resolved and must not appear in unresolved_terms.\n3. Use ambiguous only when the request itself explicitly leaves incompatible meanings unresolved. Otherwise use resolved.\n4. Add forbidden identifiers only for explicit prohibitions such as 'do not use'. Never infer a prohibition from provider capabilities or availability.\n5. Return only the schema-conforming JSON object and no explanation."
      },
      {
        "role": "user",
        "content": "CAPABILITIES\n- v07-p18-prepare: Assemble sensor inspection source packet; Collect the source material needed for sensor inspection.; aliases=['gather sensor inspection inputs', 'prepare sensor inspection packet']\n- v07-p18-verify: Validate sensor inspection source packet; Check the assembled sensor inspection material for correctness.; aliases=['check sensor inspection inputs', 'verify sensor inspection packet']\n- v07-p18-deliver: Publish sensor inspection verified brief; Release the checked final brief for sensor inspection.; aliases=['issue sensor inspection brief', 'release sensor inspection summary']\n- v07-p18-archive: Archive sensor inspection verified brief; Preserve the checked sensor inspection brief for long-term retention.; aliases=['retain sensor inspection brief', 'store sensor inspection summary']\n\nTRUST POLICIES\n- v07-p18-ordinary: ordinary sensor inspection assurance; Standard trust is sufficient for this sensor inspection request.; aliases=['normal sensor inspection assurance']\n- v07-p18-elevated: elevated sensor inspection assurance; Elevated trust is mandatory for this sensor inspection request.; aliases=['high assurance for sensor inspection']\n\nARTIFACT CONTRACTS\n- v07-p18-json: sensor inspection machine-readable JSON; Return the final sensor inspection result as JSON.; aliases=['sensor inspection json output']\n- v07-p18-signed-pdf: sensor inspection signed PDF; Return the final sensor inspection result as a signed PDF.; aliases=['signed sensor inspection document']\n\nAGENTS\n- v07-p18-backup: backup sensor inspection publisher\n- v07-p18-primary: primary sensor inspection publisher\n- v07-p18-verifier: sensor inspection source verifier\n- v07-p18-preparer: sensor inspection source preparer\n\nREQUEST\nFor this sensor inspection job, gather the inputs, check the packet, and issue the brief with normal sensor inspection assurance as sensor inspection JSON output. Do not prepare the sensor inspection packet."
      }
